11. PAGE STRUCTURE REQUIREMENTS
---------------------------------------------------------
ALL webpages for Old Money application must follow this structure:

HEADER SECTION:
- Fixed top position
- Title: "Old Money"
- Navigation buttons (Refresh, Close) with tooltips
- Buttons positioned right-aligned, icon-first design

DESCRIPTION SECTION (REQUIRED):
- Appears immediately after header
- Brief description of page purpose
- Example: "Calculate compound interest over time with yearly breakdowns"
- Uses "old money" aesthetic typography
- Light background color (#F7F7F2)

MAIN CONTENT SECTION:
- Input fields, tables, forms, or primary content
- Responsive layout for desktop/tablet/mobile

LINKS SECTION (REQUIRED):
- Appears at bottom of content
- Links to other pages in the Old Money application
- Navigation back to homepage (index.html)
- Related pages links
- Minimal styling with hover effects

